### Localization API Testing
### Test endpoints for the backend localization system

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/localization

### 1. Get Supported Languages
GET {{apiUrl}}/languages
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get All Translations (Auto-detect from Accept-Language header - Azerbaijani)
GET {{apiUrl}}
Accept-Language: az-AZ,az;q=0.9,en;q=0.8
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Get All Translations (Auto-detect from Accept-Language header - Turkish)
GET {{apiUrl}}
Accept-Language: tr-TR,tr;q=0.9,en;q=0.8
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Get All Translations (Auto-detect from Accept-Language header - English)
GET {{apiUrl}}
Accept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.9
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Get Azerbaijani Translations (Query Parameter)
GET {{apiUrl}}?lang=az
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 6. Get English Translations (Query Parameter)
GET {{apiUrl}}?lang=en
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 7. Get Turkish Translations (Query Parameter)
GET {{apiUrl}}?lang=tr
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 8. Get Azerbaijani Translations (Path Parameter)
GET {{apiUrl}}/az
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 9. Get English Translations (Path Parameter)
GET {{apiUrl}}/en
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 10. Get Turkish Translations (Path Parameter)
GET {{apiUrl}}/tr
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 11. Get Specific Translation - Azerbaijani (common.welcome)
GET {{apiUrl}}/az/common.welcome
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 12. Get Specific Translation - English (auth.login)
GET {{apiUrl}}/en/auth.login
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 13. Get Specific Translation - Turkish (subscription.title)
GET {{apiUrl}}/tr/subscription.title
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 14. Get Specific Translation - Using Dash Notation (common-save)
GET {{apiUrl}}/az/common-save
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 15. Get Specific Translation - Nested Key (validation.required)
GET {{apiUrl}}/en/validation.required
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 16. Test Unsupported Language (Should fallback to English)
GET {{apiUrl}}/de
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 17. Test Invalid Translation Key (Should return 404)
GET {{apiUrl}}/en/invalid.key.that.does.not.exist
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 18. Get All Translations with Complex Accept-Language Header
GET {{apiUrl}}
Accept-Language: az-AZ,az;q=0.9,tr-TR;q=0.8,tr;q=0.7,en-US;q=0.6,en;q=0.5
Content-Type: application/json

